      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLAME WALLY (2) was in the minors two back (22.48) at Ballarat but ran below best last time at this track, finishing 6th. Tough to beat if on-song. GUARDIAN (8) had second look this course and distance latest and improved on her time, finishing a 4.5 lengths third in 22.82. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. LOLLY CAKE (3) filled a minor placing last start at Geelong behind Aston Rennes (23.15) in a Maiden. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Can feature again. SCROLL UP (4) is a newcomer from the Emma Scott kennel. Start all important from the squeeze box. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
